snippet.title: Garfield, Eat Your Words (1985) - Apple II MiSTer FPGA Core - GARFATHON #2
snippet.description:
Next on Garfathon is "Garfield, Eat Your Words" from 1985, an educational game for Apple II. On this one I required some assistance from people with more knowledge about US people/places than me, and just knowledge in general. Originally streamed on http://twitch.tv/srmxy

(Played on MiSTer FPGA, Apple II core.)
